{"title":"凯旋忆当年（二）","authors":["西虹","西野"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"凯旋忆当年（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西虹词  西野画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小妹妹瘦的皮包骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主的孩子肥又肥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我妈眼窝核桃深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也浑身骨包皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再过一年刚十四，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我当猪倌赚吃的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风裹雨裹光脊梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十冬腊月穿破衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每日早出又晚归，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空着肚子还挑水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗锅倒尿零杂多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三更半夜整猪食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放猪的活儿本难干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我人小猪多跑断脚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾了大猪顾小猪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑来跑去无休息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨地主孙剥皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欺压猪倌不讲理；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每日归来将我骂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拳也打呀脚也踢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他双手摸着猪肚皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨个要检查瘦和肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸着肥的点点头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见了瘦的皱双眉。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}